    "description": "Systematic h-refinement mesh convergence study performed on the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA model. Four mesh densities evaluated (coarse ~18 k elements, medium ~52 k, fine ~140 k, extra-fine ~380 k). Convergence assessed on peak von Mises stress at the screw-rod junction and on construct stiffness QoI. Richardson extrapolation applied to quantify discretization error. Study executed in Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 under the same boundary conditions as the validation simulations.",
