      "rationale": "Three benchmark problems (cantilever beam, Hertzian contact, elastic ring) reproduced within 0.3–0.8% of closed-form solutions using the same element types (SOLID186, CONTA174) deployed in the pedicle screw model. Required and achieved levels both at 2."
