      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-lot non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws with full traceability (serial numbers, lot certificates). Constructs split across two independent laboratories (n=6 Lab A, n=5 Lab B) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Sample size exceeds minimum threshold for the required credibility level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
