      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 (5 mm offset, standard UHMWPE block). Only one test condition evaluated due to resource constraints; required level 3 not achieved. This factor is below the required level and constitutes a known gap in the credibility evidence base."
    },
