      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry verified by CAD overlay with fixture drawings. Material inputs matched to coupon data from same lot. Load application point and constraint conditions confirmed equivalent to test setup by independent review. Equivalency formally documented in model validation report."
    },
    {
